        "answer": "A",
        "explanation": "$\\tan(45-30) = \\frac{1 - \\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{3}}{1 + \\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{3}} = \\frac{3 - \\sqrt{3}}{3 + \\sqrt{3}} = 2 - \\sqrt{3}$."
