        "explanation": "$\\cos\\theta = \\frac{12}{13}$. $\\sin(2\\theta) = 2\\sin\\theta\\cos\\theta = 2 \\cdot \\frac{5}{13} \\cdot \\frac{12}{13} = \\frac{120}{169}$."
